headline: 4 Consumer Product Stocks to Keep an Eye on Despite Market Challenges
summary: The Zacks Consumer Products - Staples industry is navigating a tough consumer environment and elevated SG&A costs. Nevertheless, PG, CL, KMB and CLX are leveraging innovations to drive growth.
